credit.credit-words: Sing to the Lord, exalt Him high, Who spreads His clouds all round the sky; There He prepares the fruitful rain, Nor lets the drops descend in vain.
But saints are precious in His sight, He views His children with delight; He sees their hope, He knows their fear, And looks, and loves His image there.
